name: Alejandro Martinez
profile_summary: This user is a 34-year-old man who uses He/Him/His pronouns and identifies as straight. He's of Hispanic/Latino ethnicity and a practicing Catholic with moderate political views. He strongly values family, education, and career growth. Originally from Gilroy, California, he now resides in Los Angeles. As a software engineer in the tech industry, he's well-educated with a graduate degree from the University of California, Berkeley. He's a monogamist looking for a long-term relationship and wants children someday, though he doesn't have any currently. In terms of lifestyle, he's an active individual who doesn't engage in smoking, marijuana, or drug use but enjoys drinking occasionally. He speaks English and Spanish, and enjoys hiking, cooking, and traveling in his leisure time. His zodiac sign is Sagittarius and his MBTI personality type is ENFP. He's a dog lover but isn't a fan of smoking or drugs, and he's looking for someone who shares similar preferences.
